    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Enrich contact records with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API 24/7 for Multi-Tool Agent (01295)\n\n**Pattern:** Data Enrichment ┬Ę **Level:** Advanced ┬Ę **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nEnrich contact records with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API 24/7 for Multi-Tool Agent (01295). It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual multi-tool agent is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule ŌåÆ Init Cursor ŌåÆ Page Loop ŌåÆ Remove Duplicate Requests ŌåÆ Upsert Harvest into HubSpot ŌåÆ Tally Harvest Stats ŌåÆ Sort Requests Newest First ŌåÆ ŌĆ”\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to data enrichment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating multi-tool agent in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: ­¤¤” entry ┬Ę ­¤¤¬ AI ┬Ę ­¤¤½ actions ┬Ę Ō¼£ utilities ┬Ę ­¤¤® outputs ┬Ę ­¤¤ź error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath ŌĆö read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "ca550522-1bc4-ce83-6168-3350848a294e",
      "name": "­¤ōś Workflow Overview"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ­¤ø¤ Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3├Ś with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail ŌåÆ context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.",
        "width": 360,
        "height": 260,
        "color": 3
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -230,
        -20
      ],
      "id": "8c30dcf5-6f6d-37fa-2830-7411594411a1",
      "name": "­¤ø¤ Error handling & retries"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ŌÅ▒ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait ŌĆö throughput drops, reliability rises.",
        "width": 360,
        "height": 260,
        "color": 1
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        190,
        -20
